snippet.textDisplay:
she lived In a city which is 450 km away from my home..  I saw her in August 2014 for the 1st time(TU), with open hair she was walking off our university classroom.. i still remember her smile & Bunny teeth.. I was so curious to know about her that with the help of her friend I put myself in into her Facebook friendlist...  
and talk begins...... we talked a lot on facebook and Instagram but never exchanged our numbers.. presently she is residing in my city. just 20km away from my home.. we still chat.. but never meet because she has no feelings for me... I love her though she doesn't care about it.. I understand her mind , she doesn't have anything towards me and it's okay for me.. it's been 10 years...  I've learned to understand things... she will be my dream forever cz I know I'm not gonna get her in this life.. 
it's 2.15 AM, the room is dark...
Last month, she wore a traditional attire of the bodo tribe & I'm watching that pic now...
 kaisa pyaar hai yaaro, 10 saal se khatam hi nehi ho raha hai.... Kaash dono taraf se ho jaata..... 😔  
Jaunga kahan....main to hoon yaahan...
